headline: Q3 Earnings Roundup: PENN Entertainment (NASDAQ:PENN) And The Rest Of The Casino Operator Segment
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at PENN Entertainment (NASDAQ:PENN) and the best and worst performers in the casino operator industry.
